that you had some,

267
00:10:09,242 --> 00:10:11,278
um, memory-jogging techniques.

268
00:10:11,311 --> 00:10:13,313
Perhaps some mental exercises
I could do,

269
00:10:13,346 --> 00:10:15,215
preferably, while I'm sleeping

270
00:10:15,248 --> 00:10:17,284
