273
00:10:22,255 --> 00:10:23,924
Oh, please,
I can win at anything.

274
00:10:23,957 --> 00:10:25,325
Let's start there.

275
00:10:25,358 --> 00:10:27,427
Your desire to win tells me

276
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:29,863
