on finding my lost memories?

278
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:35,002
Because that's what
I'm paying you for.

279
00:10:35,035 --> 00:10:36,870
Well, I think
we should slow down

280
00:10:36,904 --> 00:10:39,339
and focus on what
you do remember.

281
00:10:39,372 --> 00:10:42,409
You say that you keep reliving
the same thing over and over.

282
00:10:42,442 --> 00:10:43,944
Is it like,

283
00:10:43,977 --> 00:10:49,249
