your own grunt work for once.

306
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:45,238
Did you know
that Abel

307
00:11:45,272 --> 00:11:47,374
was the first soul in Hell?

308
00:11:47,407 --> 00:11:48,341
Mm, an infernal guinea pig,

309
