save the planet?

433
00:16:46,339 --> 00:16:47,474
I mean, come on.

434
00:16:47,507 --> 00:16:48,608
It was fun.

435
00:16:50,077 --> 00:16:51,478
(exhales)

436
00:16:51,511 --> 00:16:53,313
