(clears throat)

437
00:16:53,346 --> 00:16:56,049
Look. I hated Alexa's movie.

438
00:16:56,083 --> 00:16:59,152
Okay? But I would
never hurt her.

439
00:16:59,186 --> 00:17:02,322
